WorkItem.Description:
For some reason I cannot fathom, when I optimize it gets to 100% then suddenly finds that it can put a Shield into my Main Hand (thus carrying 2 shields, in some cases the same shield twice). I suspect the issue lies with the new warnings Kavan introduced for the optimizer but I don't wanna stick my foot in my mouth.
 
Attaching Character file, steps to repeat are load file, run optimize with current unreleased code.
 
I have not tested to see if other shield-bearing classes are having the same issue.
